quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,52,"And We inspired to Moses, "
  26,53,"Then Pharaoh sent among the cities gatherers{1}",footnotes:1:[Recruiters of an army to prevent the emigration of the Children of Israel.]
  26,54,"[And said], "
  27,25,"[And] so they do not prostrate to Allāh, who brings forth what is hidden within the heavens and the earth and knows what you conceal and what you declare -"
  27,26,"Allāh - there is no deity except Him, Lord of the Great Throne."
  27,27,"[Solomon] said, "